用意したurdfファイルをrvizで動かすステップ3つ

＊/robot_description(ros2topic)にlinkとjointの位置情報をパブリッシュ

ros2 run robot_state_publisher robot_state_publisher --ros-args -p robot_description:="$(cat /home/nishi/ros2_ws/src/omuni_description/models/attempt_omni.urdf)"




＊guiでjoint駆動さえるguiを表示？

ros2 run joint_state_publisher_gui joint_state_publisher_gui



＊xacro-urdf変換

ros2 run xacro xacro src/omuni_description/models/attempt_omni.urdf.xaro  > src/omuni_description/models/attempt_omni.urdf


